cdata.name: STARS
cdata.desc:
STARS is a community-driven sports trivia and prediction platform. It is a betting website that allows the participants to play skilled based casino games using cryptocurrencies and to predict the outcome of events. STARS works with an odd mechanism based on the probability of the available events.

TheSTARS (STRS) token is a Waves-based cryptocurrency developed by Stars. The tokens can be used when performing the predictions and/or playing the casino games at the platform. In addition,STARS token can be bought and sold on the Turtle Network Exchange and Fortune Exchange.
